headline: Where Will Honeywell Be in 1 Year?
summary: Honeywell (NASDAQ: HON) is a $130 billion market cap industrial Goliath.  It operates businesses that span from automation to aerospace to advanced materials.  Here's what you need to know if you're looking at Honeywell right now.
